title: Arab Christian Lectures By Fr. Matta El Maskeen (Mathey The Poor
description:
These are the christian lectures by Fr. Matta El Maskeen, one of the icon monks in the world lived in Egypt. The lectures vary from 1973 to 2001, in Arabic. Enjoy
